    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "ACCIDENTS FROM THE SHADOWS",
        "Description": "Welcome agent, local authorities have reported that a group of pirates have been attacking and kidnapping residents of the island to torture them looking for the lost treasure map that belonged to their ancestors. Their deaths must appear to be accidents so as not to arouse suspicion and avoid a civil war on the island. This contract was created by members of the HITMAN community known as josthin and Thornicroft.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as josthin and Thornicroft.",
